text: "Out of Control" is a 1999 song by The Chemical Brothers and is the third single from their third studio album Surrender. It went to number 21 in the United Kingdom, number 26 in New Zealand, number 16 in Scotland and number 18 in Spain. It also charted on the Billboard Dance Club Songs chart. ==Track listings== ==References== Category:1999 songs Category:The Chemical Brothers songs
